# Gitignore for marketing/
#
# Strategy: commit the specs (README, routine prompts), ignore the dynamic outputs
# (daily reports, lead lists, drafts, intel). Outputs may contain Reddit usernames,
# competitor screenshots, or unpublished post drafts — don't want those in a public repo.
#
# We ignore the *contents* of these folders (using /*) but NOT the folders themselves,
# so the .gitkeep markers commit and the directory structure is preserved.

reddit/karma/*
reddit/leads/*
reddit/research/*
reddit/drafts/*
reddit/intel/*

# But keep the placeholders so the directory structure is documented in the repo
!reddit/karma/.gitkeep
!reddit/leads/.gitkeep
!reddit/research/.gitkeep
!reddit/drafts/.gitkeep
!reddit/intel/.gitkeep
